content: A day of my life: watch youtube and make $TUBE.EarnTube is a newly released project.It based on 'View-to-Earn' project, and consisting of the character NFT and several items are applied to it,You will perform the mission. And when you complete missions, you get tokens($TUBE)(Items have a boost effect)These tokens can be used to buy new items, which can then be cashed out.The project is based on polygon(or ETH, Sol), and if the project is successfully settled in the future,expanding to other blockchains.(ETH, SOL )EarnTube will be released as an app, and both IOS and Android are supported.For more details, please check our website as a link.Discord-    https://discord.gg/earntubeTwitter     https://twitter.com/earntubeioWebsite    https://earntube.ioPre-register now!(It will be very grateful for your participation and feedback.)
